Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能寄来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得要写信哦 小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 郡山先生 内田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等谁寄来的信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想起以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎~ 小姐的过去对我来说是最近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为大人以后 比起回忆 忘记的事情更多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生也忘记了很多东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经忘记过重要的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活到现在 遇到的人数不胜数 肯定也会有忘记的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会忘记大叔你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你啊 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 大家都要过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不是有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 只是来看看小姐你 对吧 内田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 小遥 最近有没有什么奇怪的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使说奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议的事太多了 已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:04:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真厉害啊 我可是差点心脏都停止掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果发生什么事了 打电话给我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是我们做的到的 绝对会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10点前对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐很精神 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近发生的都是些不得了的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起大人来 小孩的适应性更强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 内田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被当作奇异现象处理了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个当作海市蜃楼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生难道不生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是大人的想法罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使会被杀 也当作没有看见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 好了啦 只是和小姐说话的时候回想起了一些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 以后准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接去和佐佐木委员长谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去说阻止Magic Circle计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时侯是只靠直觉生存的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为大人以后 知道了社会的组成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了只靠智慧生存
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的那个 一般是不可能出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还是出现了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的啊 大家不都是亲眼看到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 手机里又没拍到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灵 是巨大的灵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是不是都忘记了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为谁都没有谈起那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:06:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人都相当排斥 谈那个的话题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们看到的也是事实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次出现的话 我就用这个来拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 大家肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 最近特别有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是那个的原因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把这个带过来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要用这个摄影机把它拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就可以很精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是只要有一个足球就精神极了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种花很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样花朵不是很可怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是瞄准你的脸的 为什么会击中花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说 你究竟有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你说什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装傻 快说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 这家伙躲过了我的攻击 已经恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么到现在都没有变身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是正常的燕雀 早就反击了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说教授真的许可了Magic Circle计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木教授你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田君 你从学生时代就一直没有改变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是太急于下结论了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学可不是结论…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不是结论 而是假定”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学时代已经听过很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有一个 “科学是人类的财产 不是用来赚钱的东西”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢 内田君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道 当那个科学成为金钱的一瞬间\N就成为了经济学增长的幅度了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再和筱原谈一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:09:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是相信你的报告书上 对发生时空重迭的绝对临界的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 想要再稍微保护一下你的研究的假定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在非常感谢您 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我停止Magic Circle计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木 你该不会是认真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子势能反应已经被认可 而那样的情况假定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为绝对临界阻止委员会\N对Magic Circle计划的解除实验是不承认的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有了很大的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝临什么的啊 只是个装饰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对政府的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为说什么“要好好为国民的安全和地球的环境考虑”之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想你能在脱离世俗的研究室里生活 是谁的功劳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是好好的考虑一下比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这家伙来撬开量子力学的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以引起新的网络革命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不仅仅在通信方面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界整个将为之改变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是该变化的时候了 可以创造出全新的世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪张嘴说要停止的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有说要停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说要重新审视一遍计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 态度转的真快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要停止的话 你的研究室也就没有经费了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要另人讨厌的说什么重新审视一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就全面推进好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有量子学的黛博士证明的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能引起危险的实验的许可…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不能批准的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳果然很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是泳衣果然还是很土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝了水 感觉很不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇很不擅长游泳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是勉强你到水里去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在地面上生活就可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说借口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能指望藤原认真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小绫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 遥 你到哪里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小绫 是小绫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黛家的小遥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不见了呢 过的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 很久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来这里旅游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是暑假 所以过来观光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫 好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们从东京搬走的时候 你可非常寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥 记得再写信过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 那个人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥要搬家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我绝对会写信给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 我们约好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是你在东京时候的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 小绫 不过完全被她忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意了 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有我们不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是吃惊了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的友情可是永远的 never end哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}never end：永远不完结
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你是最危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 真是失礼 藤原君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈拜托我买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我必须走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 不是就买个东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的好迟钝啊 买东西什么的肯定是骗人的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真的?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来相当受了冲击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 稍微去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是 大家一起去的话 那家伙可能反而更加心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将实行龙之转矩的逆算固定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚才你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆算固定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩的量子数据已经得到保存
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够按照数据再构成灵子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩就能够来到这拉库利玛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了进行逆算固定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须最大限度的使用拉库利玛的灵子计算机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 界线就会一时消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那个时候 被香格里拉袭击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…除此以外还有什么别的方法吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将进行逆算固定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:14:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 遥的话出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等她可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 在遥的房间等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心和果汁在平常摆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是郡山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被下了行动终了的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说让我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田一案 到这里就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝临的佐佐木委员长辞职了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接任的叫户部都下的老头 把你从绝临里面除名了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一直用的手段了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 进入三号站台了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定从哪里到三了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定是从六号站台到三号站台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认六到三
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要慌张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人豆腐 好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相田 你在哪里 相田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相田 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀的同僚很干脆的被当作自杀处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察没有好好的调查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件是牵扯到驻外大使的间谍事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能公开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是过分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使对媒体泄露 也会被筱原压下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我可不会再放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使会死也不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 内田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们能做的就是寻找黛博士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是那么喜欢的外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆的笑脸、声音 渐渐的都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥的外婆去世 是在2年前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没有办法啊 对去世的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能记得那么清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都忘记了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小绫忘记了我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我忘记了外婆一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会忘记的事也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和遥第一次见面的事 至今还记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是二年级的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和巴隆 阿姨一起 到我家里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 遥是很健忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还好好的记着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬到这里来 非常不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 佑温柔的安慰我 让我非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家应该在遥的家里等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候也牵着手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多余的事却记得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆算固定 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波动观测 开放中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,概率0.001%开始上升中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固定率 0.2%上升中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据传送 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空间转移 倒数计时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:20:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原 捣乱可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鸢 刚才的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇 不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀 下次一起去爬山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是 那也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了时空变化率高的地方调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风振动的声音越来越响
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆算固定率 72%
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆算固定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:22:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红秧 他准备把遥带到拉库利玛去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空在歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 这个波动是 至今没有过的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拉库利玛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近的话会被卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.37,0:22:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:33.94,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}眠れない夜　秒針の音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:40.21,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}冷蔵庫が虚空に唸る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:46.04,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}ブラインド越しの月が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:49.94,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}満ち欠けるようにいつかは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:55.79,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}痛みは温もりに変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:24:06.79,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}時の舟　どこへ流されても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:11.13,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}めぐり逢えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:16.64,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}傷痕から夜明けの足音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.74,0:24:19.90,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}溜め息より密かに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.92,0:24:26.04,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}新しい毎日が降りそそぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:31.57,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}どんな空にも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.75,0:24:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.73,0:24:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏日的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.46,0:24:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年后的未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.52,0:24:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已经不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.25,0:25:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就和我一起去香格里拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.80,0:25:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.10,0:25:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能再见到你吗
